---
title: Smokey BBQ Pork & Rapid Rice with Mayonnaise, Chives & Charred Pineapple Slaw
description: These spiced pork steaks have all the flavour of smokey barbeque in a fraction of the time! With a tangy pineapple slaw, a dollop
of creamy mayo and a bed of quickly cooked rice, it's sure to become a staple speedy dinner in no time.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/smokey-bbq-pork-rapid-rice-5726edf0.jpg
